{
  "Applications in Quantum Mechanics": "量子力学应用",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "The density matrix rho for a pure state |psi> is rho = |psi> = (1/sqrt(2))(|0> + |1>), what is the (1,1) entry of rho?": "纯状态 psi > 的密度矩阵 rho 是 rho = psi > = (1/sqrt(2) (0 > + 1 > ), rho 的条目(1,1) 是什么 ?",
  "|psi> = (1/sqrt(2), 1/sqrt(2))^T. rho = |psi>.": "*psi > = (1/sqrt(2), 1/sqrt(2))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",
  "What is a 'quantum state' in the language of linear algebra?": "线性代数语言中的“量状态”是什么?",
  "A pure quantum state is a unit vector |psi> in a complex Hilbert space H with ||psi|| = 1. The Hilbert space structure (inner product, completeness) provides the mathematical framework for quantum probability.": "纯量度状态是指Hilbert 复合空间H中的单位矢量 psi>,该空间为 psi = 1. Hilbert 空间结构(内产物,完整性)提供了量子概率的数学框架。",
  "What is the 'Hamiltonian' in quantum mechanics?": "量子力学的\"Hamiltonian\"是什么?",
  "The Hamiltonian H is a Hermitian matrix (or operator) whose eigenvalues are the system's energy levels and whose eigenvectors are the energy eigenstates. It drives time evolution via U(t) = e^{-iHt/hbar}.": "汉密尔顿H是一个埃米提亚矩阵(或操作员),其精华价值是该系统的能量水平,其精华源是能量源。它通过U(t) = eiHt/hbar}推动时间演变。",
  "What is a 'tensor product' in quantum mechanics?": "量子力学中什么是“电荷产品”?",
  "The tensor product H_A (x) H_B creates the composite Hilbert space for two quantum systems. If system A is in C^m and B is in C^n, the joint system lives in C^{mn}. This exponential growth enables quantum computational advantage.": "高压产品H_A (x) H_B为两个量子系统创建了复合的Hilbert空间。如果系统A在Cm,而系统B在Cn,则联合系统在Cmn。这种指数增长可以带来量子计算优势。",
  "What is 'quantum entanglement' mathematically?": "什么是数学意义上的“量的缠绕”?",
  "An entangled state |psi> in H_A (x) H_B cannot be factored as |a> (x) |b>. Entanglement is detected by the Schmidt rank: if the state has more than one term in its Schmidt decomposition, it is entangled.": "H_A (x) H_B 中缠绕的状态 psi > 不能算作 a > (x) b > 。 缠绕由施密特等级检测到: 如果该国在施密特分解中有一个以上的术语, 它会被缠绕 。",
  "What is the 'Schmidt decomposition'?": "什么是\"史密特分解\"?",
  "The Schmidt decomposition is the SVD applied to the coefficient matrix of a bipartite quantum state. The Schmidt coefficients lambda_i quantify entanglement: a state is entangled iff it has more than one nonzero Schmidt coefficient.": "施密特分解法是适用于两边量子状态的系数矩阵的SVD。施密特系数 lambda_i 量化缠绕:如果一个国家有一个以上非零施密特系数,它就会被缠绕。",
  "What is 'quantum decoherence' in terms of density matrices?": "就密度矩阵而言,什么是“量不一致性”?",
  "Decoherence causes the off-diagonal elements (coherences) of the density matrix to decay, transforming a pure state rho = |psi>": "不一致导致密度矩阵的离对角元素(一致性)衰变,改变纯状态 rho = psi >",
  "What is the 'trace distance' between two quantum states?": "两个量子状态之间的“距离”是多少?",
  "The trace distance D = (1/2)||rho - sigma||_1 measures the maximum probability of distinguishing two quantum states. It uses the trace norm (sum of singular values) and ranges from 0 (identical) to 1 (orthogonal).": "跟踪距离 D = (1/2) rho - sigma1 测量了区分两个量子状态的最大概率。 它使用跟踪规范( 单值总和) , 范围从 0 (同号) 到 1 (正数) 不等 。",
  "What is a 'quantum channel' mathematically?": "数学上“ 量子通道” 是什么?",
  "A quantum channel E is a linear map on density matrices that is completely positive (preserves positivity even on extended systems) and trace-preserving (trace(E(rho)) = 1). It describes the most general physical evolution of a quantum state.": "量子信道E是密度矩阵上的线性地图,完全正(即使在扩展系统上也保留积极性)和痕量保留(trace(E(rho))=1),它描述量子状态的最一般物理演变。",
  "What is the 'fidelity' between two quantum states?": "两个量子状态之间的“忠诚”是什么?",
  "Fidelity measures how close two quantum states are. For pure states, F = ||^2. For mixed states, the general formula involves matrix square roots. F ranges from 0 (orthogonal) to 1 (identical).": "对于纯状态,F = = 2。对于混合状态,一般公式涉及矩阵平方根。F 从0(横向)到1(相同)不等。",
  "A quantum computing researcher prepares a 2-qubit state |psi> = (1/sqrt(3))|00> + (1/sqrt(3))|01> + (1/sqrt(3))|10>. What is the reduced density matrix of the first qubit obtained by tracing out the second qubit?": "量子计算研究者准备2-qubit state psi > = (1/sqrt(3)) 00 > + (1/sqrt(3)) 01> + (1/sqrt(3)) 10>。通过追查第二Qbit获得的第1Qqit的降低密度矩阵是什么?",
  "rho_1 = trace_2(|psi> = |0>(1/sqrt(3)|0>+1/sqrt(3)|1>) + |1>(1/sqrt(3)|0>): rho_1,00 = 1/3+1/3=2/3, rho_1,11 = 1/3, rho_1,01 = 1/3*1 = 1/3, rho_1,10 = 1/3. So rho_1 = [[2/3, 1/3],[1/3, 1/3]].": "rho_1 = 追踪_2(psi > = 0>(1/sqrt(3)01/sqrt(3)1>)+ 1>(1/sqrt(3)0>):rho_1,00 = 1/3+1/3=2/3,rho_1,11 = 1/3,rho_1 01= 1/3*1 = 1/3,rho_1,10 = 1/3。so rho_1 = [[2/3,1/3,1/3],[1/3,1/3]]。",
  "A quantum simulation researcher models a spin chain with nearest-neighbor interactions. For 4 spins, the Hilbert space has dimension 2^4 = 16. The Hamiltonian H = J * sum(Z_i Z_{i+1}) is a 16x16 matrix. What is a key property that makes this Hamiltonian tractable?": "量子模拟研究者模型是一个具有近邻相互作用的旋转链。 对于四个旋转, Hilbert 空间的尺寸为 24 = 16. 汉密尔顿 H = J * sum( i i+1} ) 是一个 16x16 矩阵。 使这个汉密尔顿能够移动的关键属性是什么?",
  "Each Z_i Z_{i+1} term is diagonal in the computational basis, making H sparse (actually diagonal in this case). Even for non-diagonal interaction terms, the tensor product structure makes H very sparse, with only O(n*2^n) nonzero entries instead of 2^{2n}.": "”i i+1} 术语在计算基数中是对角的, 这使得 Hs 稀疏( 此处实际上是对角 ) 。 即使是非对角互动术语, 高压产品结构也使得H 非常稀疏, 只有 O( n* 2n) 非零条目, 而不是 22n} 。",
  "A quantum cryptography researcher studies the BB84 protocol. Alice sends qubits in either the Z-basis ({|0>, |1>}) or X-basis ({|+>, |->}). What is the inner product <0|+>?": "量子加密研究者研究 BB84 协议 。 Alice 以 Z-basis (0 > , 1) 或 X-basis (, - ) 发送 quits。 什么是内产物 < 0 ?",
  "|+> = (|0> + |1>)/sqrt(2). So <0|+> = <0|(|0> + |1>)/sqrt(2) = (1 + 0)/sqrt(2) = 1/sqrt(2). This means measuring a |+> state in the Z-basis gives |0> with probability |1/sqrt(2)|^2 = 1/2.": "* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *",
  "A quantum hardware engineer designs a controlled-Z gate (CZ), which applies a phase of -1 to |11> and leaves other states unchanged. What is the CZ matrix?": "量子硬件工程师设计了一个控制Z门(CZ),该门的阶段为-1至11>,其他状态保持不变。 CZ矩阵是什么?",
